subject: How to generate JUnit HTML reports in Android
msgSnippet: Hi All, I am using ant build system to build my Android project, and I am trying to generate HTML reports by using junitreport ant task. Its generating HTML
messageBody:
Hi All,

I am using ant build system to build my Android project, and I am trying to generate HTML reports by using junitreport ant task. Its generating HTML and XML reports but all are empty.

Can any one please suggest me. How to get HTML reports in Android.

Thanks,
Vamsi.
